::Hot Rod::

He saw the attacks coming. He braced his hands on Vehements shoulders,
and fliped over. He then got some distance from that bot. He was strong.
The Hot Rod could feel a un mistakable life force. A being from his
past. He walked up to the bot.
"Unicron, its time for round two."
He sent two optics, three plasma charges, and two missiles at Unicron.
